<codeline lineno="147"><highlight class="stringliteral">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="148"><highlight class="stringliteral">title:<sp/>Start</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="149"><highlight class="stringliteral">---</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="150"><highlight class="stringliteral">A:<sp/>Hey,<sp/>I&apos;</highlight><highlight class="normal">m<sp/>a<sp/>character<sp/>in<sp/>a<sp/>script!</highlight></codeline>
