<codeline lineno="152"><highlight class="normal">-&gt;<sp/>What</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&apos;s<sp/>going<sp/>on</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="153"><highlight class="stringliteral"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>A:<sp/>Why<sp/>this<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>demo<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>script<sp/>system!</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="154"><highlight class="stringliteral"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>B:<sp/>And<sp/>you&apos;</highlight><highlight class="normal">re<sp/>in<sp/>it!</highlight></codeline>
