<codeline lineno="158"><highlight class="normal">[[Leave|Leave]]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="159"><highlight class="normal">[[Learn<sp/>more|LearnMore]]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="160"><highlight class="normal">===</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="161"><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="162"><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="163"><highlight class="normal">All<sp/>we<sp/>need<sp/>to<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">do</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>now<sp/>is<sp/>add<sp/>in<sp/>two<sp/>more<sp/>nodes,<sp/>the<sp/>Leave<sp/>and<sp/>LearnMore<sp/>nodes.<sp/>We</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&apos;ll<sp/>add<sp/>a<sp/>little<sp/>bit<sp/>of<sp/>conversation<sp/>in<sp/>to<sp/>Characters<sp/>A<sp/>and<sp/>B<sp/>just<sp/>to<sp/>differentiate<sp/>between<sp/>the<sp/>two<sp/>nodes.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="164"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="165"><highlight class="stringliteral">```</highlight></codeline>
